room_title: Escape room "The Vault" by PuzzleWorks in Minneapolis - St. Paul
room_address: 550 Vandalia St. Suite 311 Saint Paul, MN 55114
room_description: All those emails you've been receiving are true - the exiled prince of Yurgmurgistan does indeed have treasure locked away in the national bank, and he needs your help to get it. In exchange for your services, he's offering a handsome reward. Can you break in and break out while the guard's away?
